01:03:00.377 --> 01:03:01.443
- Make you jealous, Ryan.

01:03:01.445 --> 01:03:02.444
- Trying to make
me jealous, huh?

01:03:02.446 --> 01:03:03.945
- Come on, Jay.

01:03:04.314 --> 01:03:05.413
Walk away.

01:03:06.850 --> 01:03:09.117
- I'll see you on the field.

01:03:10.053 --> 01:03:12.053
