You know what?

01:04:06.059 --> 01:04:07.142
It's a great way for me to deal

01:04:07.144 --> 01:04:09.377
with the stresses of the office.

01:04:09.379 --> 01:04:10.445
Here try.

01:04:14.985 --> 01:04:15.917
- Alright.

01:04:19.423 --> 01:04:20.989
- BOSS: Nice.

01:04:22.125 --> 01:04:23.124
- Does feel good.

01:04:23.126 --> 01:04:24.092
- See that?

01:04:24.094 --> 01:04:26.461
Work can be very stressful.

01:04:29.032 --> 01:04:30.599
- You're right.

01:04:30.601 --> 01:04:32.400
I have been under a
lot of stress lately.

01:04:32.402 --> 01:04:33.869
I don't know if you heard,

01:04:33.871 --> 01:04:36.605
but my mom's been
sick with cancer.

01:04:36.607 --> 01:04:39.074
- Sorry I didn't know that.

01:04:40.477 --> 01:04:42.110
- Yeah, thanks.

01:04:45.482 --> 01:04:47.616
- Go home, Ryan.

01:04:47.618 --> 01:04:49.284
Be there for your mom.

01:04:49.286 --> 01:04:50.185
- Thanks.

01:04:50.187 --> 01:04:51.653
Appreciate that.

