should be a writer.

01:07:41.291 --> 01:07:43.725
- So I see you're a bit
of a spiritual person.

01:07:43.727 --> 01:07:45.293
- How'd you know?

01:07:48.298 --> 01:07:49.230
Yes, I am.

01:07:51.601 --> 01:07:54.335
- My sister in-law's
big into God.

01:07:54.337 --> 01:07:55.770
- Oh, smart girl.

01:07:56.807 --> 01:07:59.307
- Well, sometimes
she gets a little

01:07:59.309 --> 01:08:01.276
