01:08:01.278 --> 01:08:06.247
- Would you prefer that
she keep it all to herself?

01:08:06.249 --> 01:08:07.849
- Yeah sometimes.

01:08:07.851 --> 01:08:11.586
- Sometimes it just
comes pouring out.

01:08:11.588 --> 01:08:13.788
- It's funny you say that.

