01:09:49.452 --> 01:09:50.417
We all are.

01:10:03.466 --> 01:10:06.901
- RYAN: I'm really
scared right now.

01:10:07.737 --> 01:10:09.404
- Don't be scared.

01:10:10.440 --> 01:10:11.839
Don't be scared.

01:10:12.642 --> 01:10:15.610
I don't want you to be scared.

01:10:15.612 --> 01:10:18.279
It's a natural part of life.

01:10:19.416 --> 01:10:21.216
I'm okay with it.

01:10:21.218 --> 01:10:23.985
- RYAN: I'm not okay with it.

