01:11:25.849 --> 01:11:26.981
I love you.

01:11:28.018 --> 01:11:29.484
I'm proud of you.

01:11:29.486 --> 01:11:30.018
- Love you.

01:11:30.020 --> 01:11:31.653
- ROSE: Love you.

01:11:35.292 --> 01:11:39.327
- IAN: Could you stay
a little bit longer?

01:11:39.329 --> 01:11:39.927
Please.

01:11:39.929 --> 01:11:41.629
- ROSE: I hope so.

01:11:44.434 --> 01:11:46.668
At that moment, Ian seemed more

01:11:46.670 --> 01:11:50.305
